424
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,040
Who wrote this?

425
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:37,640
I can't do this.

426
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,320
Kind of breaking down,

427
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,000
