521
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:21,690
Yeah.

522
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,320
I'll give you my answer tomorrow.

523
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:32,480
Alright.

524
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:44,280
Ugh, I gotta wait till tomorrow?

525
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:45,400
Because...

