571
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:21,120
Very dramatic.

572
00:22:21,320 --> 00:22:22,960
Come on, tell us.

573
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:24,160
We love it all dramatic.

574
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,240
We love this stuff.

575
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,600
So basically, we go by a...

576
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:28,040
Script.

577
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:28,760
A script setting.

578
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:29,160
Exactly.

579
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,440
